 \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ben_Davidson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Watch NBC Bay Area News free wherever you are  \\\"The amount of time that we spend racing is so small compared to the amount of time that we spend training,\\\" Davidson said.\", \"from\": 445, \"to\": 615, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 451, \"end\": 463, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KNTV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBC Bay Area\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KNTV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KNTV\"}, {\"begin\": 451, \"end\": 463, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KNTV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBC Bay Area\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KNTV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KNTV\"}, {\"begin\": 601, \"end\": 609, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Davidson_Wildcats_men's_basketball\", \"score\": 0.5925596321503168, \"rank\": 0.615580188645945, \"text\": \"Davidson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Davidson_Wildcats_men's_basketball\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Davidson_Wildcats_men's_basketball\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You have to be able to sort of fill that time.\", \"from\": 616, \"to\": 663, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's being able to keep yourself motivated and set short-term and long-term goals.\\\"\", \"from\": 664, \"to\": 747, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Both have been rowing for more than a decade.\", \"from\": 749, \"to\": 794, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Davidson was born in England and grew up in Florida.\", \"from\": 795, \"to\": 847, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 795, \"end\": 803, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Davidson_Wildcats_men's_basketball\", \"score\": 0.5925596321503168, \"rank\": 0.615580188645945, \"text\": \"Davidson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Davidson_Wildcats_men's_basketball\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpe