rg/resource/California\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Together, they punched their ticket to Paris after winning the men's double sculls at the World Rowing Final Olympic and Paralympic Qualification Regatta last month in Switzerland.\", \"from\": 969, \"to\": 1149, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1008, \"end\": 1013, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999697251956, \"rank\": 3.027481451167177e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1059, \"end\": 1071, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Rowing_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"World Rowing\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Rowing_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Rowing_Federation\"}, {\"begin\": 1137, \"end\": 1148, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"score\": 0.9890286310932928, \"rank\": 0.01107268556671729, \"text\": \"Switzerland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's something I have wanted to do since I started rowing in high school,\\\" Koszyk said.\", \"from\": 1151, \"to\": 1239, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"To actually do it and see myself there is pretty cool.\\\"\", \"from\": 1240, \"to\": 1296, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This will be Koszyk's first Olympics.\", \"from\": 1300, \"to\": 1337, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Davidson finished fourth in the men's eight at the Tokyo Olympics.\", \"from\": 1338, \"to\": 1404, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1338, \"end\": 1346, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Davidson_Wildcats_men's_basketball\", \"score\": 0.5925596321503168, \"rank\": 0.615580188645945, \"text\": \"Davidson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Davidson_Wildcats_men's_basketball\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Davidson_Wildcats_men's_basketball\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He's expecting a much different experience in Paris because there are no COVID-19 restrictions.\", \"from\": 1406, \"to\": 1501, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1452, \"end\": 1457, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999697251956, \"rank\": 3.027481451167177e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It means a lot to me to be able to go back a second time,\\\" He said.\", \"from\": 1503, \"to\": 1571, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I'd say the biggest thing is to be able to bring my family with me.\", \"from\": 1572, \"to\": 1640, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This has been a journey we have been on together since I started in 2010.\", \"from\": 1641, \"to\": 1714, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a great experience to race in Tokyo but tough to not have my family there.\", \"from\": 1715, \"to\": 1796, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am really excited to bring them with me this time.\\\"\", \"from\": 1797, \"to\": 1850, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The rowing events get underway on July 27, one day after the Opening Ceremony in Paris.\", \"from\": 1852, \"to\": 1939, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1913, \"end\": 1929, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Paralympics\", \"score\": 0.9875798867147902, \"rank\": 0.007617985491310089, \"text\": \"Opening Ceremony\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Paralympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Paralympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1933, \"end\": 1938, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999697251956, \"rank\": 3.027481451167177e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is a lot of pressure involved with it, but they are prepared,\\\" coach Nathanael Kielt said.\", \"from\": 1941, \"to\": 2038, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They put in the work.\", \"from\": 2039, \"to\": 2061, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am excited for what they can do in Paris.\\\"\", \"from\": 2062, \"to\": 2106, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2099, \"end\": 2104, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999697251956, \"rank\": 3.027481451167177e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}]}"